Date: 2026-06-30

Request: CROSS-REQ-04 - Governance & Execution Boundary Review

Workspace: `/opt/Axodus`

Versioning note: `/opt/Axodus` is not a Git repository. This review is local/unversioned unless migrated to a versioned portfolio documentation repository.

## Purpose

This review defines the current approval and execution boundaries across Axodus nuclei.

It answers who may approve, who may execute, which nuclei are non-executive, which nuclei are execution-sensitive, which approvals are required, and which actions remain blocked.

This review does not implement integrations, APIs, product functionality, MCP services, providers, governance execution, treasury execution, trading execution, DEX execution, marketplace settlement, mining payouts, lottery payouts, ACS provisioning, wallet signing, on-chain writes or production readiness.

