## High-Risk Boundary Areas

- Treasury/custody/revenue/payout authority.
- Governance proposal, voting, execution and DAO registry mutation.
- Wallet signing, private keys and account custody.
- Trading execution, exchange connectivity and withdrawals.
- DEX swaps, routing, liquidity and aggregation execution.
- Marketplace settlement, payment, minting and value transfer.
- Mining provider execution and payouts.
- Lottery randomness, prizes and payouts.
- ACS/MCP provisioning, memory access, autonomy and runtime permissions.
- Production credentials, databases, users and claims.

## Current Boundary Decision

No `EXECUTION_AUTHORIZED` classification is assigned. Every execution-sensitive action remains blocked unless a future request presents explicit owner approval, governance/treasury/security evidence, rollback/audit evidence and production boundary approval where applicable.

## Recommended Resolution Sequence

1. CROSS-REQ-05 - Portfolio Integration Assessment & Promotion Board Refresh.
2. Formalize root global docs versioning and publication ownership.
3. Formalize Treasury/Financial Core authority.
4. Define Business-to-AxodusAPP read-only consumer contract.
5. Run owner-specific boundary decisions for Marketplace, Academy, Mining, ACS, Trading, Defi, Lottery and Dex.

## Assessment

GOVERNANCE_EXECUTION_BOUNDARY_REVIEW_ESTABLISHED
